# NL Team Trends - Scripts Directory
#
# This directory is intended for Python scripts that produce reproducible
# charts, analyses, and data processing pipelines for NL team trends.
#
# Planned scripts:
# plot_pennant_timeline.py      - Generate NL championship timeline chart
# plot_win_loss_parity.py       - Create wins vs losses scatter plot
# plot_era_heatmap.py           - Generate era dominance heatmap
# plot_h2h_network.py           - Build H2H rivalry network graph
# plot_division_titles.py       - Division title bar chart
# plot_franchise_trajectory.py  - Franchise win% trajectory sparklines
# plot_single_season_records.py - Top single-season records chart
# plot_23yr_spans.py            - Sliding window 23-year span analysis
# utils.py                      - Shared data loading and processing utilities
#
# To run:
#   python scripts/plot_pennant_timeline.py
#   python scripts/plot_win_loss_parity.py